lation is driven by ExB drift. This can be resolved if\nthe observed $P_3$ periodicity is due to a beat between an ExB system and the\npulsar period. As a by-product, we identify the correct periods and spin-down\nrates for 12 pulsars, for which harmonically related values were reported in\nthe literature.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 10 Jan 2023 16:35:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-29"}
