ing. These analyses led to the following\nobservations: (i) ML developers put most of the logging statements in model\ntraining, and in non-ML components. (ii) Data and model management appear to be\nthe main reason behind the introduction of logging statements in ML-based\napplications.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 10 Jan 2023 22:48:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-12"}
